                                        &ensp; &ensp; a) Green V : If all Attachments / Remarks for that entry have been Accepted in Vouching. <br />
                                        &ensp; &ensp; b) Blue V : If All Attachments / Remarks are accepted for that entry and at least one is accepted with remarks.<br />
                                        &ensp; &ensp; c) Red V : If any one Attachments/ Remarks is Rejected for that entry.<br />
                                        &ensp; &ensp; d) Yellow V : If any Attachments / Remarks is pending to be Vouched/ Audited.<br />
                                        5.Vouching Filters shall work as "Any" and not "All".i.e.Suppose we filter Vouching Data with "Pending" Status,<br />
